   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1284, recto: (1) A reckoned solidus (2) has come (3) to me from you, (4) Enoch (son of) Daniel, in the (5) sixth year; (6) for the poll tax 1/2 solidus, (7) for the dapane 1/2 solidus.  (8) Pharmuthi 16, indiction 7.  (9) Pisrael, the headman, (10) signs.  Psate (son of) Pisrael, (11) I have drawn up this receipt.</ab>
